# Report Generator Skill

A specialized skill for generating professional reports from processed results.

## Description
This skill formats processed search results into an attractive, readable report suitable for delivery via WeChat.

## Configuration
- report_format: customizable template
- image_inclusion: enabled
- emoji_usage: enabled
- detail_enrichment: enabled
- historical_storage: enabled

## Functions
- format_report: Applies report template to results
- enrich_details: Adds additional details to select results
- validate_report: Ensures report meets quality standards
- deliver_report: Sends report to designated channel
- store_historical_report: Saves report for future reference